As per the assignment request:
1. i recreated the project based on Ldap authentication and JWT token the same way done with the 1v1 session.
2. i created the models related to the api but in WebFlux format.
3. i created the corresponding services and wrote all necessary CRUD operartions in it.
4. i created a MongoDB nonRDB on cloud and connected it to my project.
5. i created clean conveyable controllers.
6. i created a projectSecurity configuration where i gave access only for ADMIN role.
7. i created exception handling in the login service on case the admin entered his username or pass wrong.
8. i created another exception handler in MyUserService and PhotoService and AlbumService if the admin try to get an invalid id.

